        void setTemplateContent(TemplateFile template,
                        java.lang.String prefix,
                        BDO target)
        Set parameters in a template. The prefix is to allow multiple objects of the same type to be added to a template under differnet names.
        Parameters:
        template - TemplateFile to add content to.
        prefix - String prefix to be pre-pended to property/region names
        target - Object to take data from
